1. Moj ćale* je radio u Nemačkoj godinama. (My father worked in Germany for years.)
2. Ćale* mi je dao puno saveta. (My father gave me a lot of advice.)
3. Ćaliću* sam poslao pismo. (I sent a letter to my grandfather.)
4. Ćaletu* sam otkrila čudnu tajnu. (I discovered my grandfather's strange secret.)
5. Ćaletova* kuća je stara i zapuštena. (My grandfather's house is old and neglected.)